ass=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div data-id=\"540366e\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-540366e elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div data-id=\"73fb3a1\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73fb3a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-element_type=\"divider.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n			<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"></span>\n		</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n				<div data-id=\"6f54239\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f54239 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-element_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">New Portfolio Features</h3>		</div>\n				</div>\n				<div data-id=\"20d1914\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20d1914 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-element_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">Some new great features have been added to the <a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/extension/ocean-portfolio/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Portfolio</a> extension.</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n				<div data-id=\"ecca5b0\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ecca5b0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-element_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>1. It is now possible to choose to enable/disable the link and lightbox icons.</p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n				<div data-id=\"13d49ee\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-13d49ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-element_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>2. You can enable a setting to open the item image in a lightbox to the image click.</p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n				<div data-id=\"25d9d3e\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25d9d3e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-element_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>3. The lightbox script is replaced by PhotoSwipe, this new script is much better and has great features like full screen, social share, better looking, etc&#8230; This script is perfect for photographers to showcase your work in a beautful lightbox. You can check the new lightbox in live in the <a href=\"https://photography.oceanwp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Photography demo</a>.</p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n				<div data-id=\"ec9af26\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ec9af26 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-element_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"526\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/photoswipe-script-1024x526.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/photoswipe-script.png 1024w, https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/photoswipe-script-300x154.png 300w, https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/photoswipe-script-768x395.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-id=\"58e42eb5\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58e42eb5 elementor-section-boxed e